Keller Williams Bluegrass Realty - Lake Cumberland

data.description: Check out this amazing home in the sought after subdivision of Southern Hills. This beauty has .72 of an acre, large fenced in area for your fur babies or kiddos, very large deck for entertaining, and a patio on lower level with walkout access to the 2,230 Sq Ft. unfinished basement with so much potential to make it your own, man cave for entertaining, mother in law suite Etc. Main level has a very large 2 car attached garage, 4 Large Bedrooms, 2 baths, massive living room, extra sitting area, formal dining room, large stunning kitchen with stainless steel appliances, new counters and plenty of cabinetry. The master En-suite is very large with double vanity, relaxing tub and a stand up shower. Then we have an extra large dedicate laundry room with utility sink and large walk in closet. This Price, this area, this much space for entertaining, it can't be beat. Check it out for yourself!!
